Done. Created React document storage components in `web/dashboard/src/features/documents/`:

**Files created:**
- `types.ts` - Document, UploadMetadata interfaces with utility functions
- `api.ts` - API calls to storage-service (GET/POST/DELETE `/documents`)
- `DocumentCard.tsx` - Preview cards with file metadata
- `DocumentUpload.tsx` - Drag-drop file upload with progress tracking
- `DocumentViewer.tsx` - Modal viewer with PDF/image preview
- `Documents.tsx` - Main listing page with search, pagination, stats
- `index.ts` - Export file

**Features:**
- File name, size, upload date, checksum display
- Encryption status indicator
- Download button (triggers browser download via blob)
- PDF preview via iframe, image thumbnails
- Pagination (50 items per page)
- Search/filter by filename
- Stats dashboard (total docs, storage used, encrypted count)
